The native Android DrupalGap Mobile Application Development Kit for Drupal.

Installation
============

0. Complete the Android Hello World

http://developer.android.com/training/basics/firstapp/index.html

1. Make sure your AndroidManifest.xml has Internet permissions:

<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />

2. Add this line of code after the setContentView(R.layout.main) call inside the onCreate function for the App.java file:

DrupalGap drupalgap = new DrupalGap(getApplicationContext());

